From: ZhenGuo Yin <zhenguo.yin@amd.com>
Date: Fri, 18 Nov 2022 16:24:07 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1021/2236] drm/amdgpu: update documentation of parameter
 amdgpu_gtt_size
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Fixes: f7ba887f606b ("drm/amdgpu: Adjust logic around GTT size (v3)")
Reviewed-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Christian KÃ¶nig <christian.koenig@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: ZhenGuo Yin <zhenguo.yin@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_drv.c | 3 +--
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_drv.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_drv.c
index ca1d88e0115a..8f7a0b25e3bc 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_drv.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_drv.c
@@ -238,8 +238,7 @@ module_param_named(gartsize, amdgpu_gart_size, uint, 0600);
 
 /**
  * DOC: gttsize (int)
- * Restrict the size of GTT domain in MiB for testing. The default is -1 (It's VRAM size if 3GB < VRAM < 3/4 RAM,
- * otherwise 3/4 RAM size).
+ * Restrict the size of GTT domain in MiB for testing. The default is -1 (Use 1/2 RAM, minimum value is 3GB).
  */
 MODULE_PARM_DESC(gttsize, "Size of the GTT domain in megabytes (-1 = auto)");
 module_param_named(gttsize, amdgpu_gtt_size, int, 0600);
